description:
CHS Period 1 Kennedy P- Walking Simulator is a game developed by kennedyleft. It was originally released in 2022.
You can play CHS Period 1 Kennedy P- Walking Simulator on Web, Android, Linux and macOS. The game is sold via itch.io.
